  * dht upload: New -h option to select the dput upload host (Closes: #833536).
  * dht upload: Defaults to the dput default_host, not ssh-upload.

  [ Sven Bartscher ]
  * Private scripts and libraries are now shipped in /usr/lib rather than
    /var/lib.

